d;\">反擊得勁D，反擊畫面</span></span></strong>又會被現在好落力打國際戰的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"e9d56d1d22a8787c99ae2ef19db939ec23537b29","tid":1577151,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n個個去哂睇直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fa664b1f1608a88ca2887caefc0212b6f42401","tid":1577151,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:02:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9866afd88ea9392e7762171d6df5be36da60d40d","tid":1577151,"uid":202309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5b63f7d44fdde32cf9cd5a722447fb86f9e21ef3","tid":1577151,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"779d9c81e9ef231461e502b49885cc129a8eddfc","tid":1577151,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6084a8e18fc2